Package com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.spreadsheet

Class Import.Builder

java.lang.Object
com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.spreadsheet.Import.Builder
Enclosing class:
Import
public static final class Import.Builder extends Object
A builder to create the Import operation. The builder instance is created by the static method Import.excel(String).
Settings
Property Default Value To Customize
Sheets to include all sheets include(String...) or include(Pattern...)
Sheets to exclude none exclude(String...) or exclude(Pattern...)
Table name resolver Worksheet name is used as table name resolver(Map) or resolver(Function)
Left margin 0 columns left(int) or margin(int, int)
Top margin 0 rows top(int) or margin(int, int)
Skip rows after header 0 rows skipAfterHeader(int)
